descriptionHtml:
Shop for Home Furniture, Home Decor, Office Furniture and many more. All these at unbelievable prices and at your fingertips. Earlier available as a website, now to provide our customers with great user experience, we have launched our brand new app for our customers.

You can choose from over 60,000+ items at the most affordable rates and highly attentive customer service. Here are the reasons why should you shop from us.

Favorable Shipping Policy
In order to provide great customer service, we offer a great favorable shipping policy which helps customers with easy returns of the product they bought from us.

Free Shipping
Free shipping in Manhattan, Bronx, Brooklyn, Queens, and Staten Island on orders above $200.

Maximum Shipping Price $149
No matter how many products you buy on a single order, we will charge a maximum fee of $149 for the shipping.

No Sales Tax
Except for New York, We are not required to collect sales tax on deliveries throughout the US.

Wide Range of Furniture
Select from over 60K+ products. Decor your home with our extensive collection of excellent furniture.

Most Reputed & Trustworthy Brands
We work with the most reputed and trustworthy brands of the USA which guarantees the quality of the product.

Low Prices & Price Match Promise
We offer the most competitive prices, and that’s why people love us. We match the prices as well.

In-depth Product Description
We provide a detailed description of every product we sell at The Classy Home in order to serve our customers in a better way.

Favorable & Friendly Return & Exchange policy
Easy and friendly return policy in case, you aren’t satisfied with the product you receive.

Constant Communication
We provide constant communication to our customers and keep them updated with their orders and tracking of their furniture.

descriptionHtml:
Shop for Home Furniture, Home Decor, Office Furniture and many more. All these at unbelievable prices and at your fingertips. Earlier available as a website, now to provide our customers with great user experience, we have launched our brand new app for our customers.

You can choose from over 60,000+ items at the most affordable rates and highly attentive customer service. Here are the reasons why should you shop from us.

Favorable Shipping Policy
In order to provide great customer service, we offer a great favorable shipping policy which helps customers with easy returns of the product they bought from us.

Free Shipping
Free shipping in Manhattan, Bronx, Brooklyn, Queens, and Staten Island on orders above $200.

Maximum Shipping Price $149
No matter how many products you buy on a single order, we will charge a maximum fee of $149 for the shipping.

No Sales Tax
Except for New York, We are not required to collect sales tax on deliveries throughout the US.

Wide Range of Furniture
Select from over 60K+ products. Decor your home with our extensive collection of excellent furniture.

Most Reputed & Trustworthy Brands
We work with the most reputed and trustworthy brands of the USA which guarantees the quality of the product.

Low Prices & Price Match Promise
We offer the most competitive prices, and that’s why people love us. We match the prices as well.

In-depth Product Description
We provide a detailed description of every product we sell at The Classy Home in order to serve our customers in a better way.

Favorable & Friendly Return & Exchange policy
Easy and friendly return policy in case, you aren’t satisfied with the product you receive.

Constant Communication
We provide constant communication to our customers and keep them updated with their orders and tracking of their furniture.

descriptionHtml:
Shop for Home Furniture, Home Decor, Office Furniture and many more. All these at unbelievable prices and at your fingertips. Earlier available as a website, now to provide our customers with great user experience, we have launched our brand new app for our customers.

You can choose from over 60,000+ items at the most affordable rates and highly attentive customer service. Here are the reasons why should you shop from us.

Favorable Shipping Policy
In order to provide great customer service, we offer a great favorable shipping policy which helps customers with easy returns of the product they bought from us.

Free Shipping
Free shipping in Manhattan, Bronx, Brooklyn, Queens, and Staten Island on orders above $200.

Maximum Shipping Price $149
No matter how many products you buy on a single order, we will charge a maximum fee of $149 for the shipping.

No Sales Tax
Except for New York, We are not required to collect sales tax on deliveries throughout the US.

Wide Range of Furniture
Select from over 60K+ products. Decor your home with our extensive collection of excellent furniture.

Most Reputed & Trustworthy Brands
We work with the most reputed and trustworthy brands of the USA which guarantees the quality of the product.

Low Prices & Price Match Promise
We offer the most competitive prices, and that’s why people love us. We match the prices as well.

In-depth Product Description
We provide a detailed description of every product we sell at The Classy Home in order to serve our customers in a better way.

Favorable & Friendly Return & Exchange policy
Easy and friendly return policy in case, you aren’t satisfied with the product you receive.

Constant Communication
We provide constant communication to our customers and keep them updated with their orders and tracking of their furniture.
